---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="命理工具 | 八字研究所"
  description="免費線上八字排盤、合盤分析、流年運勢等命理工具，即時計算你的四柱八字命盤。"
  activePage="tools"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="tools-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="overline">命理工具</span>
      <h1>命理工具</h1>
      <p class="tools-hero-desc">探索我們提供的各種命理分析工具，從基礎排盤到進階運勢分析，一應俱全。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tools Grid -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card tool-card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">🏛️</div>
          <h3>八字排盤</h3>
          <p>輸入出生年月日時，即時計算你的四柱八字命盤。包含天干地支、五行分布、十神分析、納音等完整資訊。</p>
          <ul class="tool-features">
            <li>四柱天干地支排盤</li>
            <li>五行分布圖表</li>
            <li>十神關係解析</li>
            <li>日主強弱分析</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/tools/chart-calculator" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; width: 100%;">開始排盤</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card tool-card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">💑</div>
          <h3>合盤分析</h3>
          <p>比較兩個人的八字命盤，分析彼此的五行互補、十神關係，了解兩人之間的契合度與相處建議。</p>
          <ul class="tool-features">
            <li>雙人命盤對比</li>
            <li>五行互補分析</li>
            <li>感情相合度評分</li>
            <li>相處建議</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="btn btn--outline" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; width: 100%; opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none;">即將推出</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card tool-card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon">📅</div>
          <h3>流年運勢</h3>
          <p>根據你的命盤，分析每年的運勢走向。了解大運與流年天干地支對命盤的影響，掌握人生節奏。</p>
          <ul class="tool-features">
            <li>年度運勢分析</li>
            <li>大運走勢圖</li>
            <li>流年吉凶提示</li>
            <li>開運建議</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="btn btn--outline" style="margin-top: 1.5rem; width: 100%; opacity: 0.5; pointer-events: none;">即將推出</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container fade-up">
      <h2>從排盤開始你的命理旅程</h2>
      <p>只需輸入出生資料，幾秒鐘即可獲得完整的四柱八字命盤分析。</p>
      <a href="/tools/chart-calculator" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">立即免費排盤</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .tools-hero {
    padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--topbar-height) + 3px + 4rem) 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--near-black), var(--dark-indigo));
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tools-hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }

  .tools-hero-desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .tool-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .tool-card p {
    flex-grow: 0;
  }

  .tool-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .tool-features li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .tool-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--crimson);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
